text: Claudia Kern (born 28 January 1990) is a German water polo player. She was part of the Germany women's national water polo team at the 2008 Women's European Water Polo Championship squads, 2010 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2012 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship, and 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:German water polo players
